<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	<title>Profile Page</title>
  <link rel="shortcut icon" href="logo1.jpg">
  <link href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-wvfXpqpZZVQGK6TAh5PVlGOfQNHSoD2xbE+QkPxCAFlNEevoEH3Sl0sibVcOQVnN" crossorigin="anonymous">
  <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/dacf88b734.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-Gn5384xqQ1aoWXA+058RXPxPg6fy4IWvTNh0E263XmFcJlSAwiGgFAW/dAiS6JXm" crossorigin="anonymous">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/animate.css/3.7.2/animate.min.css">
  <link rel="manifest" href="/manifest.json">
<style>
body {
  font-family: "Lato", sans-serif;
}
.sidenav {
      height: 100%;
      width: 0;
      position: fixed;
      z-index: 1;
      top: 0;
      left: -52px;
      background-color: turquoise;
      overflow-x: hidden;
      transition: 0.5s;
      padding-top: 60px;
    }

    .sidenav a {
      padding: 8px 8px 8px 32px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 25px;
      color: teal;
      display: block;
      transition: 0.3s;
      margin-left: 30px;
    }

    .sidenav a:hover {
      color: #f1f1f1;
    }

    .sidenav .closebtn {
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      right: 25px;
      font-size: 36px;
      margin-left: 50px;
    }
    .font-size-29{
          font-size: 29px;
    }
    .projtitle{
        /*font-family: cursive;*/
        color: navy;
        font-weight: bolder;
    }
    .logo{
        width: 75%;
        height: 156px;
        margin-left: 55px;
      }
    .left,.right{
      margin-top: 50px;
        height: 1px;
        background: black;
    }
    .reducesize{
          font-size: .8rem;
    }
    .nav_img{
        width: 68%;
        position: absolute;
        left: 24%;
        bottom: 20px;
    }
    .help{
      width: 80%;
      margin-left: 20px;
    }
    ::-webkit-scrollbar{
          width: 0;
    }
    .ab1{
      margin-left: 15px;
    }
  @media screen and (max-height: 450px) {
    .sidenav {padding-top: 15px;}
    .sidenav a {font-size: 18px;}
  }
  @media (max-width:764px){
    .moveleft{
      margin-left: 20px;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="alert alert-info alert-dismissible fade show" role="alert">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-2 col-sm-2 col-2">
        <div id="mySidenav" class="sidenav">
          <img src="logo2.jpg" class="logo">
        <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="closebtn" onclick="closeNav()">&times;</a>
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="/about">About</a>
        <a href="/account">My Account</a>
        <a href="/signout">Sign Out</a>
        <img src="navigator.svg" class="nav_img">
      </div>
      <span style="font-size:30px;cursor:pointer" class="icon" onclick="openNav()">
      &#9776;</span>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-10 col-sm-10 col-10">
        <h4 class="alert-heading">Welcome <%= data.name %> !!!</h4>
        <p class="bd-lead font-weight-lighter">My name is Smriti ! I am happy to see you here. I am your Daily Planner. Plan Your Today's Events. &#128512;</p>
        <hr>
        <p class="mb-0">I believe, It would be better if we know about each other.</p>
      </div>
  </div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-4 col-1"><hr class="left"></div>
  <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-4 col-10 alert alert-warning">
    <h4 class="font-weight-light display-4 projtitle text-danger text-center">About Me</h4>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-5 col-sm-4 col-1"><hr class="right"></div>
</div><br><br>

  <div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-1 col-sm-1 col-1"></div>
  <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-3 col-8"><img src="helpful_sign.svg" class="help"></div>
  <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-7 col-10">
    <div class="moveleft">
      <span class="lead">Hi &#128075; , I'm Smriti,</span>
      <p class="lead reducesize ab1"><br>I am your personal assistant. I am here to help you out with planning your day. Each instant is precious for every person and I would help you out in planning and working out with your day. I love this world of environment &#127757;. I always want to know about the endless possibilities of humans in this world and share them with the needed one who can then rise up in their life. I would be your friend in your journey of goals.
      <br>Many great people became successful by utilizing their time effectively. As a friend, I always want you to be successfull. Here is one of the famous quote, Which I like the most. 
            <blockquote class="blockquote mb-0 lead reducesize text-center">
              <p style="margin: 5px;">" The two most powerful warriors are <code>Patience</code> and <code>Time</code> "</p>
              <footer class="blockquote-footer">Leo Tolstoy,<cite title="Source Title"> War and Peace</cite></footer>
            </blockquote>
    </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-1 col-sm-1 col-1"></div>
</div>
<br><br><br><br><br>
<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-1 col-sm-1 col-1"></div>
  <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-7 col-10">
    <div>
      <span class="lead">&#11088; Using This Platform &#11088;</span>
      <p class="lead reducesize ab1"> <br>Firstly I would Like to share few details about this platform. You can add your daily targets that need to be finished in the mentioned time. I always track about your progress from time to time and give you my thoughts about your work. I always give you constant support and help you as much as I can. Trust me you can achieve your daily targets with patience and commitment. You can view your progress in your profile section.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-3 col-12"><img src="design.svg" class="help"></div>
  <div class="col-md-1 col-sm-1 col-1"></div>
</div>


<script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.2.1.slim.min.js" integrity="sha384-KJ3o2DKtIkvYIK3UENzmM7KCkRr/rE9/Qpg6aAZGJwFDMVNA/GpGFF93hXpG5KkN" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.12.9/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-ApNbgh9B+Y1QKtv3Rn7W3mgPxhU9K/ScQsAP7hUibX39j7fakFPskvXusvfa0b4Q" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
<script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-JZR6Spejh4U02d8jOt6vLEHfe/JQGiRRSQQxSfFWpi1MquVdAyjUar5+76PVCmYl" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

<script>

